      • getIndex

        public Set<LocalDateTime> getIndex​(ImmutableStack<Object> indices)
        Returns the index of the decorated DiagnosisKeysHourDirectory. If the decorated hour directory represents the current date (today), then by default, the current hour will be excluded from the index. However, if the profile `demo` is set, the current hour will be included.
        Specified by:
        getIndex in interface IndexDirectory<LocalDateTime,​WritableOnDisk>
        Overrides:
        getIndex in class IndexDirectoryDecorator<LocalDateTime,​WritableOnDisk>
        Parameters:
        indices - A ImmutableStack of parameters from all IndexDirectories further up in the hierarchy. The Stack may contain different types, depending on the types T of IndexDirectories further up in the hierarchy.
